Maintainer: Adam T. Kocsis <adam.t.kocsis@gmail.com>
Description: The package defines the base class VirtualArray, a wrapper around lists that allow users to fold arbitrary sequential data into n-dimensional, R-style virtual arrays. The derived VirtualArray class is defined to be used for homogeneous lists that contain a single class of objects. The RasterArray and SfArray classes enable the use of stacked spatial data instead of lists.
